metadata.name: Jessica Scout
metadata.description:
A derivative of Bored Ape Yacht Club Token #1980. 

Jessica is a partner at GoldApe Snacks on Ape Street. She started her career in the 1980s at a time when female bankers were in the minority of finance professionals. Jessica has always done it her way, and focused on finding value where others were not looking. After a lucrative investment banking career, Jessica was able to retire and join the Yacht Club where she is commonly seen on her 75-foot yacht Diamond Hands.

One of the young girls that Jessica mentors is in the girl scouts. Her troop is selling cookies, and also has the option to give back to a local veteran's charity. Jessica is lending her likeness to this derivative in an effort to raise funds for this cause.
